  "detailed_description": "<h1>Roadmap</h1><p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3141720/extras/d5a4241f17042132a9fe956a3eec2092.avif?t=1773404428\" width=600 height=1980 /></span></p></p><br><h1>About the Game</h1><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Monster Battle, this is a backpack management auto-battle chess game</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >In this game, you can buy various monsters from the store and deploy them onto the field, then battle against other players!</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Strategic Construction</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > You will summon various different monsters to fight for you, so the choice of monsters is crucial!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3141720/extras/323c4d7e82ea87a93e01e8b9937c4470.poster.avif?t=1773404428\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3141720/extras/323c4d7e82ea87a93e01e8b9937c4470.webm?t=1773404428\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3141720/extras/323c4d7e82ea87a93e01e8b9937c4470.mp4?t=1773404428\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Collect Monsters</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Monsters will have different races, shapes, sizes, and rarity. The correct combination and distribution of them are the key to enhancing combat power!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3141720/extras/cf8c4dc6d1c4c4b788d8e958cec3feaf.poster.avif?t=1773404428\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3141720/extras/cf8c4dc6d1c4c4b788d8e958cec3feaf.webm?t=1773404428\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3141720/extras/cf8c4dc6d1c4c4b788d8e958cec3feaf.mp4?t=1773404428\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Fusion Evolution</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Some monsters can merge and evolve with each other through contact, giving birth to more powerful monsters!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3141720/extras/97697a2f998a442ea62e599667095442.poster.avif?t=1773404428\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3141720/extras/97697a2f998a442ea62e599667095442.webm?t=1773404428\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3141720/extras/97697a2f998a442ea62e599667095442.mp4?t=1773404428\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Player Duel</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > The enemies in the game will be the monster choices and combinations of real players. Do your best to defeat them! The ranking mode will display the strength ranking of all players.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3141720/extras/dcdd6e09f0376ff7656f8a25f43a814c.poster.avif?t=1773404428\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3141720/extras/dcdd6e09f0376ff7656f8a25f43a814c.webm?t=1773404428\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3141720/extras/dcdd6e09f0376ff7656f8a25f43a814c.mp4?t=1773404428\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Hero Skills</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > The game has added characters of different professions, each with their own unique combat style! Choose your favorite character to start fighting!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Welcome to add the game to your wish list! </strong></p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Monster Battle, this is a backpack management auto-battle chess game</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >In this game, you can buy various monsters from the store and deploy them onto the field, then battle against other players!</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Strategic Construction</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > You will summon various different monsters to fight for you, so the choice of monsters is crucial!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3141720/extras/323c4d7e82ea87a93e01e8b9937c4470.poster.avif?t=1773404428\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3141720/extras/323c4d7e82ea87a93e01e8b9937c4470.webm?t=1773404428\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3141720/extras/323c4d7e82ea87a93e01e8b9937c4470.mp4?t=1773404428\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Collect Monsters</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Monsters will have different races, shapes, sizes, and rarity. The correct combination and distribution of them are the key to enhancing combat power!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3141720/extras/cf8c4dc6d1c4c4b788d8e958cec3feaf.poster.avif?t=1773404428\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3141720/extras/cf8c4dc6d1c4c4b788d8e958cec3feaf.webm?t=1773404428\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3141720/extras/cf8c4dc6d1c4c4b788d8e958cec3feaf.mp4?t=1773404428\" type=\"video